{
    "poem_title": "Bûche",
    "author": "Théodore de Banville",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1892",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "A quoi penses-tu, pauvre bûche ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Dis-je à la bûche dans mon feu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Qu'un blanc vêtement de peluche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Environnait, comme par jeu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Pâlie et rouge tour à tour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Comme une fille en mal d'amour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "A quoi penses-tu, pauvre bûche ?\nDis-je à la bûche dans mon feu,\nQu'un blanc vêtement de peluche\nEnvironnait, comme par jeu,\nPâlie et rouge tour à tour,\nComme une fille en mal d'amour."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "La bûche répondit : Je pense,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Avec un plaisir infernal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Que la plus douce récompense",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Est mon habit de cardinal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Dont l'adorable vermillon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Brille comme un rouge paillon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La bûche répondit : Je pense,\nAvec un plaisir infernal,\nQue la plus douce récompense\nEst mon habit de cardinal,\nDont l'adorable vermillon\nBrille comme un rouge paillon."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Le froid noir, c'est moi qui le brave,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Car seule, en ce moment, j'ai chaud.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et folle, ayant quitté la cave",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Du charbonnier, sombre cachot,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Je me chauffe dans un brasier",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Aussi vermeil que le rosier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le froid noir, c'est moi qui le brave,\nCar seule, en ce moment, j'ai chaud.\nEt folle, ayant quitté la cave\nDu charbonnier, sombre cachot,\nJe me chauffe dans un brasier\nAussi vermeil que le rosier."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Chacun s'affuble de mitaines.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "En proie à l'Hiver, ce bourreau,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Blanches, les muettes fontaines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Oubliant de verser leur eau,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Avec un faste oriental",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Ont de grands plumets de cristal.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Chacun s'affuble de mitaines.\nEn proie à l'Hiver, ce bourreau,\nBlanches, les muettes fontaines,\nOubliant de verser leur eau,\nAvec un faste oriental\nOnt de grands plumets de cristal."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Ne pouvant porter de voilettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Les messieurs tristes, dont les nez",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Ressemblent à des violettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Regrettent parfois d'être nés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Ailleurs qu'au pays où Brazza",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Dans l'air enflammé s'embrasa.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ne pouvant porter de voilettes,\nLes messieurs tristes, dont les nez\nRessemblent à des violettes,\nRegrettent parfois d'être nés\nAilleurs qu'au pays où Brazza\nDans l'air enflammé s'embrasa."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Quant aux femmes, trésor des hommes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Ces languissantes Éloas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Obtiennent, pour de fortes sommes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Des écharpes et des boas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Comme en a pu voir Paul de Kock,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Faits avec des plumes de coq.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quant aux femmes, trésor des hommes,\nCes languissantes Éloas\nObtiennent, pour de fortes sommes,\nDes écharpes et des boas\nComme en a pu voir Paul de Kock,\nFaits avec des plumes de coq."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Moi que, seule, contre la bise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Défend le calorique sain,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Je reste, pour qu'on me courtise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Rose, comme le bout du sein",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Que, parmi des touffes de lys,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Baisait le chasseur Adonis.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moi que, seule, contre la bise\nDéfend le calorique sain,\nJe reste, pour qu'on me courtise,\nRose, comme le bout du sein\nQue, parmi des touffes de lys,\nBaisait le chasseur Adonis."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Je règne sur mon lit de bronze,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Princesse qu'il faut envier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "En mil huit cent quatre-vingt-onze",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Et dans cet horrible janvier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Car je sens dans ma braise en fleur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Deux mille degrés de chaleur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je règne sur mon lit de bronze,\nPrincesse qu'il faut envier,\nEn mil huit cent quatre-vingt-onze\nEt dans cet horrible janvier,\nCar je sens dans ma braise en fleur\nDeux mille degrés de chaleur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Tout en admirant le prodige,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Après ce discours si complet,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Voilà qui va des mieux, lui dis-je,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et ton éloquence me plaît.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Ta douce fierté me surprit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Mais, bûche, as-tu beaucoup d'esprit ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout en admirant le prodige,\nAprès ce discours si complet,\nVoilà qui va des mieux, lui dis-je,\nEt ton éloquence me plaît.\nTa douce fierté me surprit,\nMais, bûche, as-tu beaucoup d'esprit ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "C'est là que je flaire une embûche.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Fût-ce un auteur du plus grand vol,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Un homme qu'on appelle Bûche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Est rarement un Rivarol,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Et sans doute il semblerait fort",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "De le confondre avec Chamfort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est là que je flaire une embûche.\nFût-ce un auteur du plus grand vol,\nUn homme qu'on appelle Bûche,\nEst rarement un Rivarol,\nEt sans doute il semblerait fort\nDe le confondre avec Chamfort."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "C'est bon, dit la bûche hautaine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Qui parlait selon son humeur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Comme parlent chez La Fontaine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Les objets quelconques, — rimeur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Glorieux du vin que tu bois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Je le sais bien, je suis en bois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est bon, dit la bûche hautaine,\nQui parlait selon son humeur,\nComme parlent chez La Fontaine\nLes objets quelconques, — rimeur\nGlorieux du vin que tu bois,\nJe le sais bien, je suis en bois."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Mais que de gens font des tirages",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "De leurs portraits coloriés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Et, pour se garer des orages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Mettent des chapeaux de lauriers",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Sur leurs têtes pâles d'émoi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Qui sont aussi bûches que moi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais que de gens font des tirages\nDe leurs portraits coloriés\nEt, pour se garer des orages,\nMettent des chapeaux de lauriers\nSur leurs têtes pâles d'émoi,\nQui sont aussi bûches que moi !"
        }
    ],
    "corpus": "mel"
}